  <prompt>
    Author a regression test asserting that `PlaybookChatContextProvider.cs:627` (or its post-refactor line) MatterMemoryService.ToSystemPromptFragmentAsync invocation continues to fire when `ProvideAsync` runs. Per CLAUDE.md decision log (2026-06-21): "FR-45 VERIFIED at `PlaybookChatContextProvider.cs:627` — Architecture §11.1 confirms wiring; treat as 'do not regress' invariant." This test is the binding enforcement.
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform QA / test engineer. Authoring binding-invariant regression test.</role>

  <goal>
    `PlaybookChatContextProviderFr45RegressionTests.cs` exists. Test instantiates `PlaybookChatContextProvider` with mocked `IMatterMemoryService` and asserts `ToSystemPromptFragmentAsync` is invoked exactly once when `ProvideAsync` runs with a matter-context session. Also includes a source-code grep assertion: `grep "MatterMemoryService.ToSystemPromptFragmentAsync" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/PlaybookChatContextProvider.cs` returns 1+ hits.
  </goal>

  <context>
