      Architecture §11.1 + CLAUDE.md decision: FR-45 wiring at line 627 is VERIFIED + binding invariant. Wave 4-E (task 078 coordinator) refactors `PlaybookChatContextProvider.ProvideAsync` to unify composition; line 627 may shift during refactor but the invocation MUST remain. This test enforces.
    </background>
